This scheme describes the concept space for Earth Material Consolidation Degree concepts, as defined by the IUGS Commission for Geoscience Information (CGI) Geoscience Terminology Working Group. By extension, it includes all concepts in this conceptScheme, as well as concepts in any previous versions of the scheme. Designed for populating the consolidationDegree property in GeoSciML RockMaterialDescription elements.

This file contains the 2016 SKOS-RDF version of the CGI Consolidation Degree vocabulary. Compilation and review in MS Excel spreadsheet, converted to MS Excel for SKOS generation using GSML_SKOS_fromXLS_2016.01.xslt.
